Class Throttle.ByTime<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • hu.akarnokd.reactive4java.reactive.Throttle.ByTime<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - the value type
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Observable<T>
    Enclosing class:
    Throttle

    public static class Throttle.ByTime<T>
extends Object
implements Observable<T>
    Creates and observable which fires the last value from source when the given timespan elapsed without a new value occurring from the source.

    It is basically how Content Assistant popup works after the user pauses in its typing.

    Author:
    akarnokd, 2013.01.16.
